snippet: The main opposition group, Renamo, said Friday that it would challenge results showing the governing Frelimo party to be the likely winner of presidential and legislative elections.
abstract: Mozambique's main opposition group Renamo says it will challenge results showing governing Frelimo party to be likely winner of presidential and legislative elections.
lead_paragraph: The main opposition group, Renamo, said Friday that it would challenge results showing the governing Frelimo party to be the likely winner of presidential and legislative elections.
